PEOPLE ex rel. HALL, Appellant, v. McDONALD et al., Assessors, Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fourth Department. May 18, 1894.) Certiorari by John Hall against Ira McDonald and others, assessors.

Argued before HARDIN, P. J., and MARTIN and MERWIN, JJ.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs.
